The,Public,Insight,Network,helps,connect,newsrooms,with,public,sources,It,gives,editors,reporters,and,producers,access,to,thousands,of,people,and,helps,them,find,those,with,knowledge,relevant,to,the,story,at,hand,Members,of,the,public,are,invited,to,become,public,sources,with,the,assurance,that,nothing,they,share,will,be,published,without,explicit,permission,The,Public,Insight,Network,provides,a,RESTful,API,that,allows,users,to,push,and,pull,data,to,and,from,the,Network,programmatically